OL,3,CBristol City Council refuses to join
OL,4,Crevolt over asylum seeker hotels
OL,6,FBristol City Council won't be
OL,7,Fchallenging the government over the
OL,8,Fuse of hotels for asylum seekers,
OL,9,Fdespite indications that a
OL,10,Fcontroversial court ruling this week
OL,11,Fcould trigger council revolts across
OL,12,Fthe country.
OL,14,FOn Tuesday, the High Court decided
OL,15,Fthat asylum seekers should be removed
OL,16,Ffrom the Bell Hotel in Epping, after a
OL,17,Fchallenge led by the local
OL,18,FConservative authority, following a
OL,19,Fwave of anti-migrant protests.
