OL,3,CBristol City Council refuses to join
OL,4,Crevolt over asylum seeker hotels
OL,6,FIt's led to real concerns that others
OL,7,Fwill follow suit, with public
OL,8,Fsentiment increasingly divided over
OL,9,Fthe use of hotels for people seeking
OL,10,Fasylum.
OL,12,FIn the West Country, Bristol has been
OL,13,Fa hotspot for public clashes in recent
OL,14,Fmonths, while two years ago it was a
OL,15,Fhotel in Newquay that became the
OL,16,Fepicentre of anti-migrant sentiment in
OL,17,Fthe South West.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
