OL,3,CBristol City Council refuses to join
OL,4,Crevolt over asylum seeker hotels
OL,6,FOutside of Bristol, hotels in East
OL,7,FDevon, Somerset and Swindon house the
OL,8,Fmost asylum seekers in the West
OL,9,FCountry, but so far there is little
OL,10,Findication any of these local
OL,11,Fauthorities will be pursuing legal
OL,12,Faction after the ruling in Epping.
OL,14,FBut the hotel figures, along with
OL,15,FTuesday's High Court ruling - and the
OL,16,Fgrowing threat of protests across the
OL,17,Fcountry - present the Home Office with
OL,18,Fa real dilemma.
