OL,3,CBristol City Council refuses to join
OL,4,Crevolt over asylum seeker hotels
OL,6,FThe government has a legal duty to
OL,7,Fhouse destitute asylum seekers while
OL,8,Ftheir claims are being dealt with, but
OL,9,Fif it becomes a legal nightmare,
OL,10,Fministers will have to scramble to
OL,11,Ffind alternatives.
OL,13,FThe Bibby Stockholm barge on Portland
OL,14,Fwas seen as another accommodation
OL,15,Foption, but one that Labour was put
OL,16,Funder huge pressure to scrap, not
OL,17,Fleast because of reports pointing to
OL,18,Fpoor conditions on board.
