OL,3,CBristol City Council refuses to join
OL,4,Crevolt over asylum seeker hotels
OL,6,FThis summer has seen a real effort by
OL,7,Fthe government to look tough on
OL,8,Fillegal migration, with measures
OL,9,Fannounced to criminalise social media
OL,10,Fvideos that advertise small boat
OL,11,Fcrossings and the manufacturing of
OL,12,Ffake passports.
OL,14,FThe Home Secretary Yvette Cooper
OL,15,Fblames the previous Conservative
OL,16,Fgovernment, and says Labour "inherited
OL,17,Fa broken immigration and asylum
OL,18,Fsystem".
